metadata.title: Bald Eagle Banding

creators.name: Wildlife Service (USFWS), Oil Spill Administration Office

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This theme contains coverages of bald eagle nest locations at which birds were banded and fitted with radio transmitters. It also includes calculated gross movement of the eagles from the nest where they were banded to the Copper River Delta. Scale is 1:63,360.
